---
title: Bocconcini Romesco Pasta with Cavatappi and Parsley
description: This DIY sweet and savoury Spanish romesco sauce coats every inch of curly cavatappi.  Add fresh bocconcini pearls to bring perfect bounce and an extra layer of texture to tonight's perfect vegetarian main.
